metadata.description: Access plots of land within the metaverse. Expand your territory, or merge multiple Metapasses to increase the total size of your world. Become a land broker, split your Metapass into smaller land plots to begin selling or renting smaller plots of land. Early access to all METAVS Alpha features. Learn more at docs.metavs.com/utility/metapass
metadata.name: Genesis Metapass #1
